##### Workaround

::: {#c76270f9 .cell execution_count=15}
``` {.python .cell-code}
def extract_catalog_url_from_job_logs(job_logs) -> str:
    prefix = r"result 'l2-ard/catalog.json': v.generate_public_url()='"
    log_with_catalog_url = next(
        iter(l.message for l in job_logs if "catalog.json" in l.message)
    )
    catalog_url = log_with_catalog_url.removeprefix(prefix).split("'")[0]
    return catalog_url
```
:::


```{.python}
